{"tid":688540,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"小米 8 發布會又整假野？偷相扮自己野？","createTime":"2018-06-03T10:26:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-04T11:32:41.000Z","uid":51701,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"4c4ca4368584047708899bf5da3e7ccdc557fba1","tid":688540,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T10:26:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2086368/小米%208%20發布會造假？相片都被找出來了\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fezone.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Farticle%2F2086368%2F%E5%B0%8F%E7%B1%B3%25208%2520%E7%99%BC%E5%B8%83%E6%9C%83%E9%80%A0%E5%81%87%EF%BC%9F%E7%9B%B8%E7%89%87%E9%83%BD%E8%A2%AB%E6%89%BE%E5%87%BA%E4%BE%86%E4%BA%86&d=HqBAyDIyCWllCqrZAG2iz8VakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=86b28297\" target=\"_blank\">https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2086368/小米%208%20發布會造假？相片都被找出來了</a><br />\n詳見內聞<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n剛剛在深圳發佈的小米 8 功能出色，<a href=\"http://ezone.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fezone.hk&d=HqBAyDIyCWllCqrZAG2iz8VakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=cb3d37a3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">ezone.hk</a> 都覺得幾吸引。不過，剛剛中國就有網站玩大踢爆，指責小米發布會介紹小米 8 AI 相機的<del>「微整型」</del>美顏功能介<del>造假</del>又呃人。雖然小米尚未有回覆，但<ins>反正記者看了來源圖，就是信了</ins>。大家一齊來看看相片來評評理。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2085000/2086368/20180602_AIR_02_600.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2085000%2F2086368%2F20180602_AIR_02_600.JPG&h=8020d093&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2085000/2086368/20180602_AIR_05_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2085000%2F2086368%2F20180602_AIR_05_600.jpg&h=92e7bc10&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2085000/2086368/20180602_AIR_04_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2085000%2F2086368%2F20180602_AIR_04_600.jpg&h=0942f07f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2085000/2086368/20180602_AIR_06_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2085000%2F2086368%2F20180602_AIR_06_600.jpg&h=e5796ee0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7b27d52352e853b958bcda4a677ae73edb984207","tid":688540,"uid":165782,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T10:30:40.000Z","msg":"屌米<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4dd098103623fa9a110fd2428456f04aa7482ea7","tid":688540,"uid":20658,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T10:36:43.000Z","msg":"乜撚都假垃撚圾"},{"pid":"88a4c87b7f6d1e5c721602061c336af1c5d34cd0","tid":688540,"uid":36791,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T10:37:40.000Z","msg":"支那人講少句大話都到死㗎！"},{"pid":"ca2387a8fb3df2a429fa17f8028237b2885d3702","tid":688540,"uid":164092,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T10:44:22.000Z","msg":"佢已經聰明過華為，大家放過佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fccd484caef481cbb0cfc8d29b6cb81b61a1f4ec","tid":688540,"uid":20658,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T12:01:24.000Z","msg":"推到多啲人知屌米咁撚賤"},{"pid":"3980b40e9a66f0a401ef380f0b7b11ab6eeb8684","tid":688540,"uid":55951,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T12:11:46.000Z","msg":"支那人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd3158ec986a3e452e5458ec052b08364a0ec726","tid":688540,"uid":20658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T12:19:23.000Z","msg":"賤過西"},{"pid":"9c434235f9b42cbccd7c343a6c35dc46a9f45eea","tid":688540,"uid":155374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T16:33:12.000Z","msg":"唔知講咩好，依家話佢抄人、造假、垃圾都好，都係好似幫緊佢宣傳，因為佢本身就係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n而且屌米請班打手為求曝光率，係唔理正面定負面嘅野都會拎嚟炒作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f99b567421b84f31cb6bc4536a7bebb3bf2c013b","tid":688540,"uid":20658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9c434235f9b42cbccd7c343a6c35dc46a9f45eea","tid":688540,"uid":155374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T16:33:12.000Z","msg":"唔知講咩好，依家話佢抄人、造假、垃圾都好，都係好似幫緊佢宣傳，因為佢本身就係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n而且屌米請班打手為求曝光率，係唔理正面定負面嘅野都會拎嚟炒作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T16:36:34.000Z","msg":"咁都要屌撚死佢架"},{"pid":"83e4b8a388e4185f6417d010d504ec8df3dacb7e","tid":688540,"uid":155374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f99b567421b84f31cb6bc4536a7bebb3bf2c013b","tid":688540,"uid":20658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9c434235f9b42cbccd7c343a6c35dc46a9f45eea","tid":688540,"uid":155374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T16:33:12.000Z","msg":"唔知講咩好，依家話佢抄人、造假、垃圾都好，都係好似幫緊佢宣傳，因為佢本身就係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n而且屌米請班打手為求曝光率，係唔理正面定負面嘅野都會拎嚟炒作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T16:36:34.000Z","msg":"咁都要屌撚死佢架"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T16:50:57.000Z","msg":"小米8手機發佈會上星期係深圳舉行，當日混亂安排原本已經惹來唔少媒體不滿，點知發佈會內容仲俾內媒同網友連環踢爆造假！<br />\n<br />\n事源小米創辦人雷軍當日係台上hard sell，話小米8係現時唯一於Antutu 跑分高達30萬嘅手機，足足拋離對手OnePlus 6 成4萬幾分。講到咁犀利，大家緊係要試試佢，點知唔試由自可，一試就見真章，會後好多媒體跑分都只係得25萬左右，同大多數旗艦機跑分差唔多。<br />\n<br />\n除咗跑分唔足，有網友仲發現，發佈會上AI微整形美顏嘅model相，原來只係偷圖，根本唔係用小米8拍攝。<span style=\"color: red;\">而微博用戶 「@手機中國」發佈，聲稱用小米8外景拍嘅風景相，其實都只係用Sony單反拍攝再加水印。</span><br />\n<br />\n今次俾人捉到正，所以小米官方都好快認咗衰仔。<span style=\"color: red;\">原來跑分上30萬，係要同高通合作優化後嘅MIUI先做到，不過更新版就仲未出。</span>至於張P圖...<span style=\"color: red;\">小米就話從來無講係用小米8影嘅，只係「原理示意圖」，風景相就仲無辜，因為係人地發錯喎。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180603/58273752\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180603%2F58273752&d=HqBAyDIyCWllCqrZAG2iz8VakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=4d78e3d0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180603%2F58273752&h=edbf44f5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180603/58273752</a>"},{"pid":"d26ce44932e37011213400dc999e61942b855731","tid":688540,"uid":58335,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T16:51:07.000Z","msg":"手機台班支那賤種打死又扮睇唔到架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e18ee1bba75a663f3a1e64234d05cc1f926d4ae","tid":688540,"uid":20658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T16:54:13.000Z","msg":"符合蟈情"},{"pid":"2f6f203243f79fead20cbfed3094ee26e502536c","tid":688540,"uid":80072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T17:21:17.000Z","msg":"其實點會醒到用stock picture"},{"pid":"86023fc290ca58e7b9757c1bf37c9e7e28fad7d4","tid":688540,"uid":21378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T04:58:40.000Z","msg":"跑分 其實預咗假<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4343761040620a